caption:
Set out across the water… La Mauricie National Park offers a whole range of beautiful places to relax. Little known to visitors, Alphonse, Écarté and Soumire lakes provide the perfect backdrop for observing fauna amidst an awe-inspiring landscape. Just launch your canoe and get out your binoculars to take in the sights! 📷 by @sebastienpaquette
